# MAITRI: Research References & Technical Bibliography
**Project ID 25175 | ISRO SIH 2025 | Astronaut Well-being Assistant**

## 1. EMOTION RECOGNITION DATASETS

### 1.1 Facial Expression Databases
- **FER2013** (Facial Expression Recognition 2013)
  - Source: Kaggle - https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/msambare/fer2013
  - Content: 35,887 grayscale 48x48 pixel facial images
  - Classes: Angry, Disgust, Fear, Happy, Sad, Surprise, Neutral
  - Citation: Goodfellow, I., et al. (2013)

- **RAF-DB** (Real-world Affective Faces Database)
  - Source: http://www.whdeng.cn/RAF/model1.html
  - Content: ~30,000 facial images with diverse emotional labels
  - Notable: Real-world conditions, multiple annotators

### 1.2 Speech Emotion Databases
- **RAVDESS** (Ryerson Audio-Visual Database)
  - Source: https://zenodo.org/record/1188976
  - Content: 24 professional actors, 7356 recordings
  - Emotions: Neutral, Calm, Happy, Sad, Angry, Fearful, Disgust, Surprised
  - Citation: Livingstone, S. R., & Russo, F. A. (2018)

- **TESS** (Toronto Emotional Speech Set)
  - Source: https://tspace.library.utoronto.ca/handle/1807/24487
  - Content: 2800 audio recordings by 2 actresses
  - Emotions: Anger, Disgust, Fear, Happiness, Pleasant Surprise, Sadness, Neutral
  - Citation: Dupuis, K., & Pichora-Fuller, M. K. (2010)

- **CREMA-D** (Crowd-sourced Emotional Multimodal Actors Dataset)
  - Source: https://github.com/CheyneyComputerScience/CREMA-D
  - Content: 7,442 audio-visual clips from 91 actors
  - Emotions: Anger, Disgust, Fear, Happy, Neutral, Sad

